== What I did to configure it ==

    # edit libyahoo2.c touse pager_port 80
    # edit aim.h to use PORT 80
    
    > ./configure --prefix=~/bin/bitlbee
    > make
    > make install-etc install
    > gcc bitlbeed.c bitlbeed
    # edit ~/bin/bitlbee/etc/bitlbee/motd.txt
    # edit ~/bin/bitlbee/etc/bitlbee/bitlbee.conf
    > bitlbeed -p6669 -n1 ~/bin/bitlbee/sbin/bitlbee


